								"name": "Shapechanger",
								"time": "1 Action",
								"uses": 1,
								"reset": "Long Rest",
								"desc": "As an action, you can polymorph into a medium sized creature with a CR equal to half your level. You gain temporary hit points equal to half the hit points of the chosen creature. Any equipment you are wearing or carrying isn’t transformed. You revert back to your true form if your temporary hit points are reduced to 0."
