								"save": "Wisdom",
								"dc": 18,
								"effect": "charmed",
								"desc": "As an action you can force one creature you can see within 30 feet to make a Wisdom saving throw or be magically charmed for 1 day."
							},
							{
								"name": "Absorption",
								"desc": "You can absorb the energy of a Creature you have intercourse with. Whenever a creature cums on or inside you, you can absorb their energy. To do so, roll a 3d6. You can choose to regain an amount of hit points equal to the roll, or instead regain 3 spell slots of your choice. The maximum level of the slot you can regain is equal to half your level (rounded up) and can't exceed 5th level."
							},
