								"time": "1 Action",
								"attack": true,
								"damage": "1d6+4 slashing damage",
								"desc": "Your claws are natural weapons. You can use them to make a melee attack instead of an unarmed strike. If you hit with them, you deal slashing damage equal to 1d6 + your Dexterity modifier."
